tation Form):** The base dictionary form (infinitive for verbs, base noun for nouns) was identified for each word, considering prefixes and suffixes (e.g., 'አለመብላቱ' to 'አለመብላት', 'ያውጀው' to 'ማወጅ').\n\n5.  **PROTOCOL: THE TRANSLATOR (Nuance Expansion):** Comprehensive English synonyms were provided for each root.\n\n6.  **PROTOCOL: THE GRAMMARIAN (Linguistic Tagging):** Each word was assigned a high-level part of speech (Noun, Verb, Conjunction, Adjective).\n\n7.  **PROTOCOL: THE FILTER (Size Constraint):** The single-character word 'ም' (from 'ጭራቅም') was discarded as per the protocol requiring words to be at least 2 characters long.\n\nNo words were discarded due to being meaningless (Protocol 2) after corrections. The corrections made were based on strong contextual and morphological evidence, ensuring the integrity of the dataset.","input_words":["ታገልክ","አለመብላቱ","ለፈጠረውና","ለባረከው","ያውጀው","እየተሳፈሩ","ቅማቸውን","ጭራቅም","እንዳያደንቅ","አሣሪው","ያሰጧቸው","በመወቀሳቸው","እንዲሰነዝሩብሽ","እንዲሳለቅብሽ","ለጎዳናዋ","ከጉዳና","አለመንደፍ","የትራንፖርትን","ከአኃዛዊ","ካሰልቀቀ","በለውጧ","በኖሩበትና","አክለውልኛል","ሱጓዙ","ስለሰሎሞን","ብልኅነትና","ለንግሥተ","ልትጋጭ","ታጸድቀዋለች","ያልጎበጠና"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"663bdd3d-2735-4d12-a64e-8f85eb492ff7","created_at":"2026-03-04T08:47:48.484107+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_15/chunk_0427.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ጣት","word":"ጣቷ","synonyms":["finger","digit"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መሸለም","word":"ከተሸለመበት","synonyms":["to award","to be awarded","to honor","to bestow"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Verb","root":"ማቃለል","word":"የምናቃልልበት","synonyms":["to lighten","to simplify","to make light of","to ease","to belittle"],"importance":8},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ሞሪስኮ","word":"ከሞሪስኮዎች","synonyms":["Morisco"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Verb","root":"መዝጋት","word":"ተዘጉት","synonyms":["to close","to shut","to seal"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፉኩሺማ","word":"የፉኩሺማ","synonyms":["Fukushima"],"importance":7},{"pos":"Ver